  description: "concurrent.futures ThreadPoolExecutor.__init__.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__ check in cfcode68 namespace — wave 237 theme: code object co_varnames type identity; co_varnames is always a tuple in CPython; ThreadPoolExecutor.__init__.__code__.co_varnames.__class__.__name__=='tuple'; NEW in extra68: first co_varnames.__class__.__name__=='tuple' check for ThreadPoolExecutor.__init__ in the cfcode68 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
  category: code
  id_prefix: cfcode68c

  columns: [id, function, args, expected, description]
